{
  "stem": "11723.5",
  "chunk_idx": 14,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "As far as I'm concerned, my daughter Vivion, my son Roger, and my granddaughter Morissa are my personal revenge against Hitler, because the first targets of Hitler were the children, because the children are the future.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And children-- and Hitler wanted to wipe us off the face of the Earth.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And if my children do not marry within the faith, we're going to disappear, and posthumously, Hitler will have won.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And one more thing I want to say is that-- recently, somebody made a comment that really bothered me-- and it was a Jewish person, too-- that the Holocaust was no different-- what Hitler did to the Jews was no different than what we did to the blacks in the 1950s.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Well, it was-- I think that's very wrong, because no-- no black person would be alive now since they're easily distinguishable.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "They couldn't hide like I did.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But also, there is the difference between the Bosnian conflict, the way the blacks were treated, and other present-day conflicts and the Holocaust.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was the first time in history that it wasn't only condoned to kill Jews, but it was the policy of the government.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they built an entire industry with the most modern technology just for the purpose of exterminating Jews.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Why?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Their only guilt was that they were Jews.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And for my descendants, one more thing-- our parents had thought that because they were living in this country, wherever they were, in Hungary, in France, or whatever, they were great patriots.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And this is their country, and they were confident in their neighbors, and they led a good life.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They couldn't believe that in a civilized society something like the Holocaust could happen.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I do not recommend paranoia for my heirs.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
